description.narrative: The Climate Change Adaptation Assessments, Thought Leadership, and Learning (ATLAS) project works to improve the quality and effectiveness of USAIDs development programs aimed at reducing climate change risks through tested and harmonized approaches to climate risk/adaptation related assessments; thought leadership on climate resilient development; and capacity building of USAID and its implementing partners.
